{"tid":2081213,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"小心旅遊禮品（5日4夜住宿）騙案","createTime":"2020-06-27T05:03:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T06:44:01.000Z","uid":67334,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f3ceb6e98054722b4f6d4b0e5ffc076abb649b72","tid":2081213,"uid":67334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T05:03:50.000Z","msg":"(借朋友AC)<br />\n頭先收到‭3892 5799‬電話<br />\n話我之前填咗一份問卷<br />\n係頭500個參與者<br />\n所以贏咗一個五日四夜嘅住宿獎品<br />\n個住宿獎品好似好吸引咁<br />\n亞洲至歐洲都可以用<br />\n佢話呢個係幫一間旅行代理公司做嘅推廣活動<br />\n（唔肯定有冇講代理，唔係記得好清楚，同埋佢有講到係邊間公司不過唔記得咗）<br />\n佢約咗我聽日上去簽收獎品<br />\n上到去會首先核對個人資料<br />\n然後會有一個展覽可以互相交流<br />\n仲話會幫我安排行程（聽到呢度開始覺得好可疑）<br />\n最後就簽收獎品<br />\n然後整個過程大約係90分鐘<br />\n佢叫我一陣下晝再打電話去拎個獎品確認編號<br />\n然後佢聽日會再打俾我同我confirm location<br />\n（因為佢喺尖沙咀有兩個location）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一聽就知係騙案啦大家一定要小心<br />\n大家呢排都冇得去旅行<br />\n加上經濟低迷好多人都失業<br />\n聽到咁嘅優惠一定好容易上當<br />\n大家一定要小心啊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource(1): <br />\n請提防電話邀約到尖沙咀聽90分鐘講座<br />\n有關講座可能與旅遊會籍或大額預繳式消費有關，持續有市民中招，請提醒朋友、同事、親戚及身邊人。<br />\n這不良銷售手法已經存在超過20年，依然每週有年青人中招，損失數千至數萬元，請提醒在家中停課的大專生、大學生和剛工作的年青人。<br />\n<br />\n敬請提防有公司藉以感謝你完成早前電話問卷調查，邀請你到某一個地方(尖沙咀?)聽90分鐘講座，之後有五日四夜或各種豐富得不合理的禮品。<br />\n<br />\n如有接聽，請務必回報<br />\n<br />\n當中或與以下情況有關<br />\n<br />\n講座時間為放工時間，一個人最疲倦的時間<br />\n疲勞轟炸／高壓推銷<br />\n跨境合約，不受香港法律保障<br />\n合約金額約8-30萬，另外還有每年大額管理費及各項行政費<br />\n3日冷靜期無法聯絡或無法解除合約<br />\n難以解除合約或需要收取大額費用(合約金額20-30%)以解除合約<br />\n如有中招請停止供款，或需向海關、消委會及議員等求助，以法律途徑處理，請PM聯絡HKJunkCall Facebook專頁咨詢。<br />\n<br />\n請提醒身邊友人、家人及青少年朋友。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkjunkcall.com/cdpush.asp?m=18&amp;l=c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkjunkcall.com%2Fcdpush.asp%3Fm%3D18%26l%3Dc&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFpR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=5f0b2b01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkjunkcall.com/cdpush.asp?m=18&amp;l=c</a><br />\n<br />\nSource(2): <br />\n中咗騙案招點算<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2061788\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2061788</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n同呢個case好似<br />\n只不過係講座換咗展覽"},{"pid":"849cb9d0818129e31c39caaf9bde734b503e2fba","tid":2081213,"uid":58717,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T05:05:35.000Z","msg":"推 呢個電話近黎好猖狂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab5bd8def40f23ea3bd145ab2664333752d57321","tid":2081213,"uid":67334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T05:06:42.000Z","msg":"推啊 唔好比呢d人賺到錢啊"},{"pid":"88cf9e3fc30c89c0f2e10d1ee7d557504efcb1a6","tid":2081213,"uid":3063,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ab5bd8def40f23ea3bd145ab2664333752d57321","tid":2081213,"uid":67334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T05:06:42.000Z","msg":"推啊 唔好比呢d人賺到錢啊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T05:09:12.000Z","msg":"唔洗啦<br />\n我又唔係弱智<br />\n你唔洗提我啵"},{"pid":"8a7f7b1bd6466ab3675b0f284df49ffc83db6361","tid":2081213,"uid":34209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T05:10:47.000Z","msg":"好耐啦 <br />\n我都試過 佢話聽完講座就走得<br />\n邊有咁荀呀 肯定到時唔俾你走 有排煩<br />\n唔好俾騙徒有機可乘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94e44c161ed3286e02050fe1ba28df0a76678a42","tid":2081213,"uid":245642,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T05:11:02.000Z","msg":"衰貪心有乜好講。正常人都知係騙局啦。"},{"pid":"8ceb149b94b657d760102e095fa8743a3031e12d","tid":2081213,"uid":67334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T05:13:22.000Z","msg":"補充番幾樣野<br />\n1. 佢有強調當中唔會有任何金錢交易<br />\n2. 有同我confirm我嘅入息水平（10,000以上或10,000以下）同工作行業<br />\n3. 通話中間有同我吹吓水好似好友善咁，強調之後見面90分鐘都係輕鬆互相交流了解<br />\n4. 打比我個係後生女，點解要咁呃人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5. 叫我一陣下晝打電話俾郭小姐 38925730 Confirm獎品編號"},{"pid":"64c2c2b1a51ff491d81efc56cd3d6dc32d7d1c24","tid":2081213,"uid":67334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88cf9e3fc30c89c0f2e10d1ee7d557504efcb1a6","tid":2081213,"uid":3063,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ab5bd8def40f23ea3bd145ab2664333752d57321","tid":2081213,"uid":67334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T05:06:42.000Z","msg":"推啊 唔好比呢d人賺到錢啊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T05:09:12.000Z","msg":"唔洗啦<br />\n我又唔係弱智<br />\n你唔洗提我啵"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T05:13:58.000Z","msg":"真係會有人信㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4095780977cd39e6f7ed46dba7e94c918b3f22a3","tid":2081213,"uid":67334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a7f7b1bd6466ab3675b0f284df49ffc83db6361","tid":2081213,"uid":34209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T05:10:47.000Z","msg":"好耐啦 <br />\n我都試過 佢話聽完講座就走得<br />\n邊有咁荀呀 肯定到時唔俾你走 有排煩<br />\n唔好俾騙徒有機可乘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T05:14:50.000Z","msg":"係啊<br />\n換過電話換過公司名換過形式<br />\n然後就重新出嚟呃人<br />\n但係真係一直都會有人信㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c270d59bc9fc37efe625207e43de82cd1561aef1","tid":2081213,"uid":67334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94e44c161ed3286e02050fe1ba28df0a76678a42","tid":2081213,"uid":245642,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T05:11:02.000Z","msg":"衰貪心有乜好講。正常人都知係騙局啦。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T05:17:39.000Z","msg":"我覺得佢比較伏嘅位係有強調冇金錢交易<br />\n好多人真係會因為咁而信<br />\n特別係同你地嘅長輩講<br />\n老一輩可能真係冇乜提防嘅意識"},{"pid":"4c999ff581fe7817bb5a320260144f24b96d4ee1","tid":2081213,"uid":216727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T0